编译kotlin
1. install kotlin
    ```
        brew update
        brew install kotlin
    ```

2. Create and run an application
    ```
        fun main() {
            println("Hello, World!")
        }
    ```

3.Compile the application using the Kotlin compiler:

    kotlinc hello.kt -include-runtime -d hello.jar
    java -jar hello.jar

or
    kotlinc hello.kt -d hello.jar
    kotlin -classpath hello.jar HelloKt
